{"tid":331733,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莊 思 敏 留 長 髮 溝 仔","createTime":"2017-07-22T12:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T12:44:42.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9ffd98b939a5ad9d6cb6da49db49de466d8682","tid":331733,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"藝人莊思敏昨日出席餐廳活動，透露剛拍完無綫兩套劇，想留回長髮，她說：「短頭髮好耐，想留番長啲，有啲女人味。（吸引異性？）都要搵啲姻緣，超過三年冇拍拖。」她謂因太忙沒時間拍拖，雖有人追，但都不適合，繼而開出條件，揚言不要小鮮肉：「鍾意啲大啲、叻啲嘅人，要食得住我好啲，教到我嘢，要搵唔容易，所以到依家未搵到。」她又透露與王子涵投資七位數字推出運動服，將放上網或健身中心賣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20170722/photo/0722-00282-014b1.jpg?t=1500724658954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170722%2Fphoto%2F0722-00282-014b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1500724658954&h=e3e2abcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcef046d0c26e01be0056123f0687d87107f74ae","tid":331733,"uid":98322,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"留長髮都救唔返個八婆樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504171431e26166918d7512f94c1f559553102e6","tid":331733,"uid":12923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"6933b4662204a43bd4a437a7fd48b6ae0449f87d","tid":331733,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}